It is impossible to judge this without talking about kazuhiro's artstyle, one which simultaneously interests and draws me away. Their work is filled with overexaggeration, a choice which for me can be a double edged sword. On one hand, potentially bland sex scenes are enhanced by distorting the human form. A normal blowjob is made to seem spectacular when the puckering of the lips is emphasized. Fue is a prime example of this. On the other hand, excessive distortion comes off as distracting and a little uncomfortable to look at, like in pages 12 and 14. Bewilderingly massive dicks are not a preference of mine, either. Ignoring everything above, however, this is a solid hentai. The FMC plays her part very well, and this is what I would judge to be a good rape femdom. 7/10.
